Module com.example.organizer
Package com.bookclub.mao

Class BookProgressMAO

java.lang.Object
com.bookclub.mao.BookProgressMAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.bookclub.iao.IBookProgressAO
public class BookProgressMAO extends Object implements com.bookclub.iao.IBookProgressAO
This class implements the IBookProgressAO interface and acts as a Mock Access Object (MAO) for managing the BookProgress objects. It handles operations related to tracking and managing the progress of books for specific users.
